-- Billionaire Carlos Slim Sees `No Currency War, Only U.S. Devaluing' Dollar
-- B y   R o d r i g o   O r i h u e l a
-- 2010-11-15T18:46:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/billionaire-carlos-slim-sees-no-currency-war-only-u-s-devaluing-dollar.html
Mexican billionaire Carlos Slim, the
world’s richest man according to Forbes Magazine, said there
isn’t a currency war taking place among countries.  “There’s no currency war, only U.S. devaluing and
devaluing,” Slim said during a presentation in Buenos Aires.  To contact the reporter on this story:
